{"tid":562683,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"真係估唔到原來做保安新年可以有咁多利👮‍♂️👍🏼👍🏼","createTime":"2018-02-16T07:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T11:41:25.000Z","uid":5995,"like":99,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4134f3af37afd8ae5a5961f4cc73a0ca3364e74e","tid":562683,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T07:01:18.000Z","msg":"今日特登唔去拜年<br />\n著晒成套老西 去做炒散保安 <br />\n一見到人就烚熟狗頭咁恭喜發財 身體健康<br />\n多數人都會比利是 唔比個d就真係有樣睇<br />\n睇落寒寒酸酸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又會迴避你眼神<br />\n一朝早已經有成過百封利是<br />\n當10蚊封都有成千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住食晏同d同事去酒樓飲茶<br />\nD茶客見到我官仔骨骨又著晒西裝咁<br />\n以為我係酒樓部長又比利是我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住又逗多廿幾封<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d210f06de5d9f70bda54969fd643b795c870a31","tid":562683,"uid":85163,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9d6ac6608501ddeffa14d1122515f05d3bfc63e","tid":562683,"uid":5995,"like":81,"dislike":5,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"D酒樓呀姐問我邊位 唔可以咁做<br />\n我屌鳩佢話你理得我邊位<br />\n你逗得我都逗得啦<br />\n新年流流要我幫你開年？<br />\n即刻嚇到個呀姐眼濕濕走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32b8ea352b916ce56b5f4ffa558b30b8780a744","tid":562683,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 